{"tid":1779733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［國際戰線要升級］丹麥傳媒：中國威脅法羅群島 若不用華為設備取消貿易協議","createTime":"2019-12-12T01:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T06:43:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"86fcf37063578a3823b2caa78ea6e198c1b16762","tid":1779733,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"唔好只係stand with hk<br />\n考慮吓幫埋俾中國打壓既國家發聲<br />\n要全球一齊支援俾中國打壓既國家/民族<br />\n<br />\n(美聯社)<br />\n丹麥傳媒報道，中國政府威脅北歐小國法羅群島(Faeroe Islands)若不同意使用中國電訊設備生產商華為供應的5G設備，將取消與該國的貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n法羅群島貿易部長亞伯拉罕森(Helgi Abrahamsen)上月15日接受該國一間電台訪問，在準備訪問期間，他的助理向他提到中國駐丹麥大使馮鐵4天前如何威脅法羅群島政府必須使用華為提供的設備，而該段私人談話被電台意外錄下。<br />\n<br />\n電台原打算播出該段錄音，但法羅政府向法庭申請禁制令，禁止公開兩人談話，以免損害與中國關係。不過，丹麥電台DR與一份報章周二報道了事件。<br />\n<br />\n法羅群島總理尼爾森(Bardur Nielsen)亦有出席上月11日與馮鐵的會面，但他表示不會談論事件。中國駐丹麥大使館未對報道置評，但中國《環球時報》引述中國外交部發言人華春瑩說，有關指控「完全不實，動機別有用心」。<br />\n<br />\n法羅群島位於蘇格蘭與冰島間，是丹麥的海外自治領地，人口只有約5萬人。丹麥首相弗雷澤里克森（Mette Frederiksen）曾表示法島群島可決定由哪個供應商供應設備建立5G網絡，但歡迎他們尋求丹麥的意見。<br />\n<br />\n華為是全球網絡安全爭議的焦點，美國指中國政府可透過華為獲取用家的數據。華為否認指控。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191212/60368489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F60368489&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnADYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=e7ef77c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F60368489&h=e870cfe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191212/60368489</a>"},{"pid":"87c6db056629cf67cb73b98a23c39a15ab647295","tid":1779733,"uid":100999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"238105c01ce2143a889a85bfd2e923c7d9718fae","tid":1779733,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【第十柒期牆紙】起來，不願做奴隸的人們<br />\nTG <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnADYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=a4c6596c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnADYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=60b45a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1778521/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1778521/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o471rTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo471rTe.jpg&h=846ba8e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef0337c4e0ccef99031b5f05efcc137fc32c8ee9","tid":1779733,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:49:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n國際戰線要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1b656dec389b0b028e401659c971909813c521","tid":1779733,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"有冇英文link"},{"pid":"1c36d3fb3e7bb30e3edfbe03867f4d56ab2cc5f1","tid":1779733,"uid":244693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"link唔該"},{"pid":"848a9801e31a60eb1269a8fac3e733d1ecc46aa0","tid":1779733,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"中國真係on9㗎喎<br />\n其他國應該要圍佢啦"},{"pid":"9c749c16698451cd506b3140281d4390fafaa641","tid":1779733,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dis